                    A 33-member mixed-voice choral ensemble dedicated to classical mastery and soulful celebration.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <h5 class="text-gold mb-3">Contact Us</h5>
                <ul class="list-unstyled text-light-muted">
                    <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-envelope me-2"></i>cexpressionevents@gmail.com</li>
